@NODE "Misc"

DRAFU+ was first programmed on an

   Amiga 500	  (68000, OS 1.2, 1,5 MB RAM, 33 MB HD),

later then on an

   Amiga 500 plus (68000, OS 2.04, 2 MB RAM, 33 MB HD),

and now on an

   Amiga 1200	  (68020, OS 3.00, 2 MB RAM, 85 MB HD).

The program was tested under OS 1.3 and OS 3.00, sometimes also under
OS 1.2 and OS 2.04.

@ENDNODE


